long_desc.thetext:
The two "previous" and "next" buttons are essential to evince functionality -
multi-pages document browsing. Setting them as important would give them more
space on the toolbar, thus setting them apart from the zoom control and making
them easier to click. Right now you have to aim a little too much :)

